Add an event listener to this Cog.

# Examples

```py
class MyCog(commands.Cog):

    def __init__(...):
        ...

    @commands.Cog.event()
    async def event_message(self, message: twitchio.Message):
        print(message.content)

    @commands.Cog.event("event_ready")
    async def bot_is_ready(self):
        print('Bot is ready!')
